metadata.name: market go brrr
metadata.description:
When animals take over, Uncle Sam is forced to role-play as a doormat at the political parties. They rename him Uncle Matt.

From "Animal World" Collection based on the universe created by Brendan S Bigney (The Nuclear Cowboy), Marine Corps Veteran, photographer, international speaker and leader, and Multi-Award-Winning Author.

Art by J.C.
